<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>Ry Jeso Tompo tsara o FFPM403</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Ry Jeso Tompo tsara ô !
 He, resy lahatra aho izao
 Fa be ny ratsy vitako
 Mandifotra ny tenako !
 Milela-paladia, re,
 Fa efa diso lehibe ;
 Esory tsy ho hitanao
 Ny mariky ny otako,
 Ampiasao ny indrafo
 Ka mamelà ny heloko !</lyrics>
<hymn_number>403</hymn_number>
<author>W.B. Bradbury</author>
</song>